panels.description: Language comparison of unary ping pong between two GKE nodes in the same cluster (each node resides on a separate VM, both VMs are located in the same compute zone). Secure connection is used.

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  (metadata->>'created')::timestamp AS time,
  (scenario->>'name') AS metric,
  MAX(CAST(summary->>'latency50' AS DOUBLE PRECISION) / 1000) as latency_us
FROM
 ci_master_results_8core
WHERE
 $__timeFilter(metadata->>'created') AND
 scenario->>'name' IN (
   'java_protobuf_unary_ping_pong_secure',
   'ruby_protobuf_unary_ping_pong',
   'node_to_node_protobuf_async_unary_ping_pong_secure',
   'node_purejs_to_node_protobuf_async_unary_ping_pong_secure',
   'csharp_protobuf_sync_to_async_unary_ping_pong',
   'cpp_protobuf_sync_unary_ping_pong_secure',
   'go_protobuf_sync_unary_ping_pong_secure',
   'python_protobuf_sync_unary_ping_pong',
   'netperf_tcp_rr'
 )
 
 GROUP BY
     time, metric;
